ne-height: 30px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; \">段子三</strong></h4><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHe&#39;, 微软雅黑, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \">去Google翻译，朗读一下内容：</p><blockquote style=\"margin: 0.7142857142857143rem 0rem; padding: 0.3571428571428571rem 0.7142857142857143rem; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 164, 239, 0.59375); vertical-align: baseline; quotes: none; background-color: rgba(0, 164, 239, 0.0976563); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHe&#39;, 微软雅黑, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; \"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; \">因为，绳命，是剁么的回晃；绳命，是入刺的井猜。壤窝们，巩痛嘱咐碰优。田下冯广宰饿妹，饿妹冯广宰呲处。壤窝们，嘱咐这缩优类缩优。开心的一小，火大的一小，壤绳命，梗楤容，壤绳命，梗秤巩，壤绳命，梗回晃。</p></blockquote><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHe&#39;, 微软雅黑, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \">标准河南话！</p><h4 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; color: rgb(0, 164, 239); font-size: 1.142857142857143rem; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHe&#39;, 微软雅黑, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; \">段子四</strong></h4><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHe&#39;, 微软雅黑, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \">Google要逆天了，打开Google翻译（英译中），输入：</p><blockquote style=\"margin: 0.7142857142857143rem 0rem; padding: 0.3571428571428571rem 0.7142857142857143rem; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 164, 239, 0.59375); vertical-align: baseline; quotes: none; background-color: rgba(0, 164, 239, 0.0976563); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHe&#39;, 微软雅黑, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; \"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; \">abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz</p></blockquote><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHe&#39;, 微软雅黑, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \">再在中文处点喇叭发音，最纯正的中式英语出现了！</p><h4 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; color: rgb(0, 164, 239); font-size: 1.142857142857143rem; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHe&#39;, 微软雅黑, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; \">段子五</strong></h4><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHe&#39;, 微软雅黑, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \">什么叫做带着东北腔的广东话，看看哥制作的Google翻译，雷死你。</p><blockquote style=\"marg